<figureCitation box="[168,285,1819,1843]" captionStart="Figure 17" captionStartId="31.[168,231,1853,1873]" captionTargetBox="[168,1419,160,1829]" captionTargetId="figure-37@31.[168,1419,160,1829]" captionTargetPageId="31" captionText="Figure 17. OROBANCHACEAE A. Esterhazya splendida. POACEAE B. Andropogon bicornis. C. A. lateralis. D. A. leucostachyus. E. Anthaenantia lanata. F. Aristida jubata. G. Arthropogon villosus." pageId="16" pageNumber="523">Figure 17F</figureCitation>
